# Minor

crime-preset-name-animal-cruelty = Animal cruelty
crime-preset-description-animal-cruelty = To inflict unnecessary suffering or harm on a non-sapient being with malicious intent.

crime-preset-name-possession-controlled-substances = Possession/Use of Controlled substances
crime-preset-description-possession-controlled-substances = To make, hold, or abuse restricted drugs or chemicals without authorization.

crime-preset-name-theft-petty = Petty Theft
crime-preset-description-theft-petty = To take non-vital or inexpensive property of another individual, organization, or common property, without consent.

crime-preset-name-damage-minor = Vandalism
crime-preset-description-damage-minor = To intentionally deface or superficially damage public or private property.

crime-preset-name-trespass = Trespass
crime-preset-description-trespass = To enter a non-secured area without permission.

crime-preset-name-disturbance = Disturbance
crime-preset-description-disturbance = To cause a public disturbance.

# Moderate

crime-preset-name-failure-comply = Failure to Comply
crime-preset-description-failure-comply = To resist reasonable orders given by an authority. This extends to authorized searches.

crime-preset-name-possession-restricted-gear = Possession of Restricted Gear
crime-preset-description-possession-restricted-gear = To hold or use non-lethal items or objects that are restricted or illegal.

crime-preset-name-damage-moderate = Damage/Destruction of Property
crime-preset-description-damage-moderate = To maliciously damage or deface public or private property or equipment.

crime-preset-name-endangerment = Endangerment
crime-preset-description-endangerment = To recklessly put yourself or others in danger, either through direct action or failure to act.

# Major

crime-preset-name-breach-arrest = Breach of Arrest
crime-preset-description-breach-arrest = To intentionally resist and flee arrest or detainment by an authorized staff.

crime-preset-name-possession-restricted-weaponry = Possession of Restricted Weaponry
crime-preset-description-possession-restricted-weaponry = To hold or use a weapon that is unlawful or contraband.

crime-preset-name-theft-grand = Grand Theft
crime-preset-description-theft-grand = To take critical or unreplaceable property of another individual or organization without consent.

crime-preset-name-damage-major = Mass Destruction
crime-preset-description-damage-major = To cause massive damage to an area or major station system.

crime-preset-name-trespass-secure = Secure Trespass
crime-preset-description-trespass-secure = To enter a secured area without permission.

crime-preset-name-assault = Assault/Battery
crime-preset-description-assault = To threaten to or to use physical force against someone without the intent to kill.

crime-preset-name-manslaughter = Manslaughter
crime-preset-description-manslaughter = To incidentally kill a sapient being without intent.

crime-preset-name-rioting = Rioting
crime-preset-description-rioting = To take part in a large group of personnel creating an unlawful public disturbance.

# Extreme

crime-preset-name-breach-custody = Breach of Custody
crime-preset-description-breach-custody = To break out of a cell or custody with the intention of escaping.

crime-preset-name-possession-restricted-weaponry-terrorism = Restricted Weaponry with Terroristic Intent
crime-preset-description-possession-restricted-weaponry-terrorism = To possess a significant amount of lethal weaponry.

crime-preset-name-kidnapping = Kidnapping
crime-preset-description-kidnapping = To unlawfully restrain, transport, control, or confine a sapient being against that individual's will.

crime-preset-name-murder-attempted = Attempted Murder
crime-preset-description-murder-attempted = To make an attempt to use physical force against someone with the clear intent to kill.

crime-preset-name-murder = Murder
crime-preset-description-murder = To kill a sapient being with malicious intent.

# Capital

crime-preset-name-refusal-mind-shield = Refusal of Mental Shielding
crime-preset-description-refusal-mind-shield = To refuse to comply with a reasonable Mind Shielding procedure.

crime-preset-name-prevention-revival = Prevention of Revival
crime-preset-description-prevention-revival = To render a body unresurrectable.

crime-preset-name-murder-mass = Mass Murder
crime-preset-description-murder-mass = To kill three or more sapient beings with malicious intent.
